Statistics of [[DPR Korea League]] in the 2002 season.
==Overview== [[April 25 Sports Club|April 25]] won the championship, [[Rimyongsu Sports Club|Rimyŏngsu]] finished second, and [[Amrokkang Sports Club|Amrokkang]] finished third. [[Pyongyang City Sports Club|P'yŏngyang City]], [[Wolmido Sports Club|Wŏlmido]], and the [[North Hwanghae Provincial College of Physical Education]] also took part in the competition.<ref name="rsssf">[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesn/nkorchamp.html RSSSF] </ref>
The 2002 edition of the [[Mangyongdae Cup|Man'gyŏngdae Cup]] was won by April 25.<ref name="rsssf"/>
