'''Li Xue''' ({{zh|c=李雪|p=Lĭ Xuě}}, born 14 April 1985) is a Chinese-born [[France|French]] [[table tennis]] player. She has competed for France at the [[Table tennis at the 2012 Summer Olympics|2012]]<ref>[http://www.london2012.com/athlete/li-xue-1065257/ London 2012] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120727232137/http://www.london2012.com/athlete/li-xue-1065257/ |date=2012-07-27 }}</ref> and [[Table tennis at the 2016 Summer Olympics|2016 Summer Olympic Games]].

