The '''Portuguese Cycling Federation''' or '''UVP-FPC''' (in [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]]: ''[União Velocipédica Portuguesa]  Federação Portuguesa de Ciclismo'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Portugal]].

The UVP-FPC is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme]].

